我们得给船体排气
Then we'll have to vent the ship.

181
00:13:12,600 --> 00:13:13,750
你疯了吗
Are you outta your tree?

182
00:13:14,980 --> 00:13:17,060
我们会失去舱内所有的氧气
We'll lose all oxygen in the cabin.

183
00:13:17,060 --> 00:13:19,370
一切希望都在修好无线电上
Everything depends on fixing that radio.

184
00:13:19,910 --> 00:13:21,110
我们在浪费时间
We're wasting time.

185
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:24,020
又来了 你又在自己做决定
There you go. Calling the shots again.

186
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:26,050
我要出去 你有意见吗
I'm going outside. You got a problem with that?

187
00:13:26,050 --> 00:13:28,090
艾莫斯 和他一起去
Amos, go with him.

188
00:13:28,090 --> 00:13:30,550
大家先等等
Let's just hold on for one second.

189
00:13:31,210 --> 00:13:32,770
我们没必要去外面
We don't have to go outside.

190
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:35,620
我们现在很安全
We're safe right now.

191
00:13:35,890 --> 00:13:37,550
把闸门打开 我们就完了
We open those doors, we're done.

192
00:13:37,770 --> 00:13:39,460
船体可能会四分五裂 我告诉你
The ship could crack apart. I'm telling you...

193
00:13:39,460 --> 00:13:41,250
-谢德 -我只是 如果我们打开闸门
- Shed? - I'm just... If we open those doors...

194
00:13:41,250 --> 00:13:42,780
听我说 听我说好吗
Please, just listen to me. Listen to me!

195
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:45,210
如果我们出去了 我们会死的
If we out there, we're gonna die.

196
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:50,190
你要休克了 你要休克了
You're in shock. You're in shock.

197
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:51,310
你知道会有什么症状
You know the symptoms.

198
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:54,020
你知道会有什么症状的 呼吸 呼吸
You know the symptoms. Just breathe. Breathe.

199
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:57,540
深呼吸 呼吸 呼吸
Deep... breathe. Breathe, breathe.

200
00:13:57,540 --> 00:13:58,590
好了
All right.

201
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,190
就是这样
There.

202
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:06,590
就像这样 冷静下来了吗
There. You chilled?

203
00:14:07,650 --> 00:14:08,720
好了
Okay.

204
00:14:08,850 --> 00:14:10,420
现在 我们要出去
Now, we're gonna go outside,

205
00:14:10,850 --> 00:14:12,480
去修好那个天线
and we're gonna fix the antenna,

206
00:14:12,560 --> 00:14:15,560
然后弄出点声音来 我们就能获救了
and we're gonna make some noise and get rescued.

207
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:17,930
-好的 -好吗
- Okay. - Okay?

208
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,420
好
Yeah.

209
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:22,040
注意脚下 伙计们 快到了
Watch your step, boys. We're on the way.

210
00:14:22,450 --> 00:14:23,930
外面情况怎么样
How's it looking out there?

211
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:26,480
不会更糟了
Well, it couldn't been worse.

212
00:14:28,430 --> 00:14:30,190
总是有更坏的可能
It can always be worse.

213
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:39,630
好吧 确实更糟
Okay. It's worse.

214
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:46,820
你不在附近队长很生气
Captain was pissed you weren't around.

215
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:48,740
她要你处理好这事
She wanted this dealt with.

216
00:14:48,780 --> 00:14:50,360
是啊 这周我真是走运
Yeah, it must be my week.

217
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,280
新的地球搭档
New Earth partner.

218
00:14:53,490 --> 00:14:55,190
吸引了所有"烫手"的案子
Drawing all the "Hot" cases...

219
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:59,320
请大家注意 空气 水和电
Your attention, please. The Air, water and power...

220
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:01,060
到时间了
Well, it's about time.

221
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,590
一个小时前你就该到了
Expected you an hour ago.

222
00:15:06,890 --> 00:15:08,950
从麦迪纳过来还挺远的 长官
It's a long hoof from the Medina, sir.

223
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:12,850
一个星期前
A week ago,

224
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:15,950
开始出现那种枯萎的绿地
those dead patches started appearing.

225
00:15:16,080 --> 00:15:19,040
我的猜测是格雷加斯的人又在偷水了
My guess is, the Greigas are stealing water again.

226
00:15:19,250 --> 00:15:20,990
有些小行星带人显然不尊重
Some Belters clearly don't respect

227
00:15:20,990 --> 00:15:24,290
绿地在空气和水循环中的重要作用
the green space's role in recycling the air and the water.

228
00:15:25,370 --> 00:15:28,210
更别说这种现象会让总督蒙羞了
Not to mention the embarrassment it causes the Governor.

229
00:15:28,990 --> 00:15:30,920
你似乎很确信是小行星带人干的
You seem sure it was Belters.

230
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:33,900
这的罪犯一般都是他们
The criminals here tend to be.

231
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:39,360
你是新来的 对吗
You're new here, aren't you?

232
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:41,030
我们会处理好的 长官
We'll get right on that, sir.

233
00:15:41,850 --> 00:15:44,220
如果谷神星上所有人都能看到这番景致
Maybe if everyone in Ceres had this view,

234
00:15:45,170 --> 00:15:46,560
他们会更尊重你
they'd respect you more.

235
00:15:57,900 --> 00:15:58,990
给你
There.

236
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:02,200
现在你可以创造自己的风景了
Now, you can make your own view.

237
00:16:24,410 --> 00:16:26,070
该死
Oh, shit!

238
00:16:37,070 --> 00:16:38,240
你是地球人
You're an Earther.

239
00:16:39,210 --> 00:16:40,860
但我都不知道你来自哪里
And I don't even know where you're from.

240
00:16:41,490 --> 00:16:44,210
再过几个小时 我们就成太空垃圾了
We're gonna be space trash in a few hours

241
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,430
你这会才想套近乎吗
and you wanna start a friendship?

242
00:16:46,610 --> 00:16:47,770
你要是觉得我们成不了
If you don't think we're gonna make it,

243
00:16:47,770 --> 00:16:49,260
那你出来干嘛
what are you doing up here?

244
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:51,950
奈奥米让我出来 我就出来了
Naomi told me to, so I am.

245
00:16:53,340 --> 00:16:56,280
就我看来 她现在是船长
As far as I'm concerned, she's the cap now.

246
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:26,570
直到弄丢我的小克莱门汀
Till I lost my Clementine

247
00:17:27,090 --> 00:17:30,150
亚历克斯 给E-12送点燃料
Alex, send me some juice to E-12.

248
00:17:31,340 --> 00:17:33,870
-我多想念她 -亚历克斯
- How I missed her... - Alex?

249
00:17:35,030 --> 00:17:36,190
亚历克斯
Alex!

250
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,960
E-12
E-12.

251
00:17:39,250 --> 00:17:40,440
收到
Copy that.

252
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,230
好了 甜心
There you go, sugar.

253
00:17:42,230 --> 00:17:43,700
你没事吧
You doin' okay up there?

254
00:17:43,770 --> 00:17:46,140
我好得就像阳光明媚的
I'm doing as good as dew on

255
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:50,130
清晨里的一颗露珠
a mornin' full of sunshine.

256
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:01,330
你和奈奥米是怎么回事
Hey, what's the deal with you and Naomi?

257
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:02,700
你俩是一对吗
You two an item or something?

258
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:04,510
一对
An item?

259
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:14,710
这不关我的事 不过...
Hey, it's none of my business, but...

260
00:18:15,310 --> 00:18:17,630
你一定以为我挺傻的吧
You must think I'm pretty stupid, don't you?

261
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,860
没错
I mean, you're right.

262
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:21,890
我闭着眼都可以
I can take a core apart

263
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:23,910
把飞船核心拆散再装回去
and put it back together with my eyes closed.

264
00:18:23,910 --> 00:18:25,150
可要问我应不应该
But ask me whether or not I should

265
00:18:25,150 --> 00:18:28,120
扯下你的头盔 把你踢走
rip your helmet off and kick you off this bucket,

266
00:18:29,050 --> 00:18:32,830
我竟然想不出一个该或是不该的理由
and I couldn't give you a reason why I should or shouldn't.

267
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,430
我只知道奈奥米不会喜欢
Except Naomi wouldn't like it.

268
00:18:46,270 --> 00:18:47,790
可以把钻头给我吗
Could you pass me the drill?

269
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:54,020
谢谢
Thank you.

270
00:18:58,110 --> 00:19:00,730
我丢了我的小克莱门汀
Then I lost my Clementine

271
00:19:02,130 --> 00:19:03,660
亚历克斯 你在干什么
Alex, what are you doing?

272
00:19:03,980 --> 00:19:06,110
我在带她回家 小圆派
I'm bringin' her home, honey-pie.

273
00:19:06,330 --> 00:19:08,970
一步 两步 我们就能在一起了
One more, two... And we'll be together.

274
00:19:09,110 --> 00:19:11,350
就再去一趟木卫三 亲爱的
Just one trip to Ganymede, sweetheart.

275
00:19:11,610 --> 00:19:14,550
别这样嘛甜心 我在回来了
Oh, don't be like that, sugar, I said I'm comin' home.

276
00:19:17,690 --> 00:19:19,630
-亚历克斯 -谢德 他怎么了
- Alex. - Shed, what's wrong with him?

277
00:19:20,020 --> 00:19:22,390
他缺氧了
He's, uh... He's hypoxic.

278
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,090
该死
Oh, shit!

279
00:19:25,090 --> 00:19:26,800
他的呼吸器不行了
His breather's crapping out!

280
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:29,230
该死 他还能撑多久
Damn it! How long can he hold on?

281
00:19:30,520 --> 00:19:33,000
该死 他快不行了
Oh, oh, shit. We're losin' him!

282
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:34,180
我们马上回来
We're coming back in.

283
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:37,060
不行 我们没有足够氧气再出舱了
Negative. We don't have enough oxygen to vent again.

284
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:39,880
谢德 照顾好他 做点什么
Shed, take care of him! Do something!

285
00:19:41,970 --> 00:19:44,350
我们在真空中 他穿着宇航服
We're in a vacuum! He's in a suit! I...

286
00:19:46,010 --> 00:19:47,310
你要我怎么做
What do you want me to do?

287
00:19:48,220 --> 00:19:49,630
没富裕的宇航服
There's no spare!

288
00:19:49,630 --> 00:19:52,070
谢德 你是个医生 像样一点好吗
Shed, you're a medic! Act like one!

289
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,250
挺住 伙计
Hold on, buddy.

290
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:58,540
听着 我要把咱俩的呼吸器连起来 好吗
Listen, I'm hooking our breathers up, okay?

291
00:19:58,540 --> 00:19:59,460
这样我们就能分享氧气了
So we can share air.

292
00:19:59,570 --> 00:20:01,270
你就可以吸我的氧了
So you can breathe off mine, okay?

293
00:20:01,350 --> 00:20:02,680
谢德 怎么样了
Shed, what's happening?

294
00:20:04,380 --> 00:20:08,270
好了 坚持住 伙计 拜托
Okay. Hold on, buddy. Come on.

295
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:13,710
坚持住 亚历克斯 拜托
Hold on, Alex! Come on.

296
00:20:15,290 --> 00:20:18,310
好了 呼吸 呼吸 亚历克斯
Yeah, there it is! Breathe! Breathe, Alex!

297
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:20,850
深呼吸
Breathe it in. Breathe.

298
00:20:24,220 --> 00:20:27,140
继续呼吸 我们真是同呼吸共命运了
Just keep breathing. We're buddy-breathing.

299
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:38,330
会没事的 没事了
It's all gonna be good. It's all good.

300
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:39,720
谢德 听着
Shed, you got this?

301
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:41,490
今天不能再死人了
No one else dies today.

302
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:44,610
如果不把无线电修好 我们今天都得死
If we don't get that radio back, we all die... today.

303
00:20:44,690 --> 00:20:46,380
好了 亚历克斯 轮到我了
Okay, Alex. My turn, buddy.

304
00:20:48,450 --> 00:20:49,930
我吸几口就够了
I just need a couple of breaths.

305
00:20:53,930 --> 00:20:55,590
这就对了
Ah, that's the stuff.

306
00:20:55,710 --> 00:20:57,470
氧气水平危急

307
00:21:00,460 --> 00:21:01,870
亚历克斯怎么样了
How's Alex doing?

308
00:21:01,950 --> 00:21:03,310
他正坚持着呢
He's hanging in there.

309
00:21:08,100 --> 00:21:09,310
那是什么意思
What does that mean?

310
00:21:09,510 --> 00:21:10,990
意思就是他在坚持着呢
Means he's hanging in there!

311
00:21:11,140 --> 00:21:13,330
继续你手头的事 快点
Get on with it. Hurry up.

312
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,580
别看它
Don't look at it.

313
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:21,780
想点别的事 好吗
Just think about something else, okay?

314
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,910
比如你的孩子 想想你的孩子
Like your kid. Think about your kid.

315
00:21:26,950 --> 00:21:28,190
他们荡着...
Swinging on a...

316
00:21:29,940 --> 00:21:31,670
荡着秋千还是什么的
Swinging on a swing or something.

317
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:34,350
你是想让我分散注意力
You're trying to distract me.

318
00:21:48,140 --> 00:21:49,270
伙计们
Hey, guys.

319
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:54,220
我们...我们的氧气要用完了
We're running out of... We're running out of air.

320
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:06,240
现在呢
Now?

321
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,780
没有信号
No carrier.

322
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:12,390
该死的
Ah, piece of shit!

323
00:22:20,370 --> 00:22:21,570
连上了
We have connection.

324
00:22:23,890 --> 00:22:25,500
马上回来
Get back in here now!

325
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,610
快
Come on.

326
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:54,220
-好了 -加压中
- Go! - Pressurizing.

327
00:23:51,350 --> 00:23:52,970
你对我做了什么
What the hell did you do to me?

328
00:23:58,300 --> 00:24:00,640
你救了我的命 兄弟
You saved my hide, partner.

329
00:24:02,110 --> 00:24:03,680
你这个疯子
You crazy son of a bitch.

330
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:06,370
不客气
Ah, no problem.

331
00:24:31,740 --> 00:24:34,690
我要把他送去月球进一步审讯
I need him sent to Luna for deeper interrogations.

332
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:40,620
他们预算有限 已经所剩无几了
They have a budget, it's already shot to hell.

333
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:42,330
我不像你 我得卑躬屈膝地
And unlike you, I have to grovel

334
00:24:42,330 --> 00:24:45,250
实现承诺才能换来连任
and promise and deliver to get reappointed.

335
00:24:45,250 --> 00:24:47,590
这和我有关系吗
This concerns me? How?

336
00:24:50,130 --> 00:24:51,160
你离掌管
You're two heartbeats away

337
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:53,430
这颗星球的政府只有一步之遥
from running the government on this planet.

338
00:24:53,850 --> 00:24:56,220
但你却不用对何人负有责任 怎么会这样呢
Yet you're accountable to no one. How does that happen?

339
00:24:56,220 --> 00:24:59,160
这孩子不是什么倒霉走私犯
This boy isn't some hapless smuggler.

340
00:24:59,510 --> 00:25:03,810
我认为外行星联盟可能是想获得隐形武器
I believe the O.P.A may be trying to obtain stealth weapons.

341
00:25:03,810 --> 00:25:05,410
不要每件事都当成外行星联盟的阴谋
Everything is not an O.P.A. plot

342
00:25:05,410 --> 00:25:07,520
如果地球都负担不起开发隐形项目
and if Earth can't afford a stealth program,

343
00:25:07,520 --> 00:25:09,250
一帮玩石头的穷鬼怎么负担得起
how can a bunch of rock-tossers?

344
00:25:09,250 --> 00:25:10,460
他们是不行
They can't...

345
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:13,650
除非找到像火星一样的合作者
Unless they've found a new friend like Mars.

346
00:25:14,040 --> 00:25:15,860
冷战就是不流血的战争
Cold war is a bloodless war.

347
00:25:16,110 --> 00:25:19,010
互不信任 彻底独立
Mutual distrust and complete co-dependence.

348
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:20,600
没人想改变这些
Nobody wants to change that.

349
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,760
至少火星人是这样
Least of all Mars.

350
00:25:24,170 --> 00:25:25,550
那是另一回事
That's another thing.

351
00:25:25,610 --> 00:25:30,320
我要你仔细监视火星上的所有武器设施
I want every Martian weapons facility under a microscope.

352
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:31,520
已经如此
They are.

353
00:25:31,650 --> 00:25:34,160
那个小行星带人会喜欢月球的重力的
You know, your Belter will like gravity on Luna better.

354
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:36,110
那恐怕是他唯一会喜欢的东西了
That's the only thing he'll like.

355
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:37,920
我担心他
I'm afraid for him.

356
00:25:38,740 --> 00:25:40,860
上帝保佑你的敌人 克里斯金
Heaven help your enemies, Chrisjen.

357
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,820
火星和小行星带
Heaven help us all

358
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:47,380
要是不分彼此的话 那就是天助你我
if Mars and the Belt decide to share a toothbrush.

359
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:52,480
我敢说那是大胆之举
Bold move, I'll give him that.

360
00:25:54,250 --> 00:25:55,520
什么
What?

361
00:25:57,630 --> 00:26:01,020
冷战结束了 这是新出现的问题
The cold war is over, this is something new.

362
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:07,830
天线可以用了 但信号还是很弱
The antenna's working but our signal's still too weak.

363
