证实坎特伯雷号是被火星摧毁
confirm that the Canterbury was destroyed by Mars.

578
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:26,560
只要这消息能到达一艘船 一个空间站
It just needs to reach one ship, one station.

579
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:28,050
就能传出去了
Then it'll spread.

580
00:41:28,050 --> 00:41:29,380
别指望了
Don't count on it.

