00:41:33,480 --> 00:41:35,200
我们处在他们的干扰范围内
Their jammers were in range.

582
00:42:37,290 --> 00:42:40,130
你们现在是火星共和国的囚犯
You are prisoners of the Mars Congressional Republic.

583
00:42:40,130 --> 00:42:41,670
